data.code:
# there are three numbers you change here
# ps1 = P(S1)
# pf1gs1 = P( F1 | S1 )
# pf2gs2 = P( F2 | S2 )

ps1 = .5 # change
pf1gs1 = .8 # change
pf1gs2 = .2 # change

# leave the rest alone
ps2 = 1 - ps1
pf2gs1 = 1- pf1gs1
pf2gs2 = 1 - pf1gs2
ps1andf1 = ps1 * pf1gs1
ps1andf2 = ps1 * pf2gs1
ps2andf1 = ps2 * pf1gs2
ps2andf2 = ps2 * pf2gs2
pf1 = ps1andf1 + ps2andf1
pf2 = ps1andf2 + ps2andf2
ps1gf1 = ps1andf1/pf1
ps2gf1 = ps2andf1/pf1
ps1gf2 = ps1andf2/pf2
ps2gf2 = ps2andf2/pf2
